## ğŸ› DEBUGGING

### Set Breakpoints
```
1. Click line number in editor
2. Red dot appears
3. Run with Debug (Shift + F9)
```

### Debug Controls
| Shortcut | Action |
|----------|--------|
| F7 | Step Into |
| F8 | Step Over |
| F9 | Resume |
| Shift + F9 | Debug |

### Inspect Variables
```
1. Run in Debug mode
2. Hover over variable
3. See value in tooltip
4. Or use Debug â†’ Evaluate Expression
```

