##  PROJECT MODULES

### main.py
- Entry point
- Orchestrates pipeline
- Calls all other modules

### data_generator.py
- `generate_economic_data()`
- Creates 864 samples
- Handles preprocessing

### model_trainer.py
- `train_models()`
- Trains 3 models
- Applies calibration

### evaluator.py
- `evaluate_models()`
- Calculates 5 metrics
- Computes ensemble

### predictor.py
- `make_predictions()`
- Predicts on sample data
- Returns probabilities

